Enum AlertCondition

  • Object
    • Enum<AlertCondition>
      • com.zebra.sdk.settings.AlertCondition
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, Comparable<AlertCondition>

    public enum AlertCondition
extends Enum<AlertCondition>
    Enumeration of the various printer alert conditions which can be set on Zebra Printers.
